spec_data.Name: php-pear-Crypt-CHAP
spec_data.Description:
This package provides Classes for generating CHAP packets.
Currently these types of CHAP are supported:
- CHAP-MD5,
- MS-CHAPv1,
- MS-CHAPv2.
